Trinity::

She giggled and lifted her right foreleg. She opened a tiny panel to 
reviel the tiny scanner inside. She looked and saw that there was a 
small clearing a few miles from where they were standing. "Hey, 
There's a clearing over there," pointing with her other paw," We can 
go over there and see if there's anything over there." She smiled and 
closed her arm panel. "What do you think?"
